paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the prevalence, characteristics, and mortality of patients with transthyretin amyloid cardiomyopathy (ATTR-CM) in the Nordic countries. However, it does not provide specific genetic variant information for the TTR gene.

challenges: The paper did not provide specific genetic variant information for the TTR gene.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper focused on epidemiological data and clinical characteristics of ATTR-CM but did not include specific genetic variant data for the TTR gene.
